2. Common Injury Rehab Protocols
Complete protocol library:
- Shoulder: Rotator cuff, frozen shoulder, labral
- Knee: ACL, MCL, meniscus, patellofemoral
- Back: Disc herniation, facet joint, SI joint
- Ankle: Lateral sprain, Achilles tendinopathy
